docstring:
"""
 Error checking functions for GEOS ctypes prototype functions.
"""

functions.docstring: "Return the last C argument's value by reference."
functions.name: last_arg_byref

functions.docstring: "Check the status code and returns the double value passed in by reference."
functions.name: check_dbl

functions.docstring: "Error checking on routines that return Geometries."
functions.name: check_geom

functions.docstring: "Error checking on routines that should not return -1."
functions.name: check_minus_one

functions.docstring:
"""
    Error checking for routines that return explicitly sized strings.

    This frees the memory allocated by GEOS at the result pointer.
    """
functions.name: check_sized_string

functions.docstring:
"""
    Error checking for routines that return strings.

    This frees the memory allocated by GEOS at the result pointer.
    """
functions.name: check_string
